Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.09,0:00:06.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! I came to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.10,0:00:08.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:18.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:20.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.03,0:00:25.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:13.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you got here early.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.95,0:01:15.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get my calligraphy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:17.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It arrived ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:23.56,STAR3,,0000,0000,0000,,STAR
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:23.56,Name 3,,0000,0000,0000,,Seishuu\NHanda
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:27.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As huge as it is, it sure looks grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:27.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:34.19,MX Handwritten,,0000,0000,0000,,STAR
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:33.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying it wouldn't \Nlook grand if it was small?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.34,0:01:34.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's{\i0} how you took it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.93,0:01:36.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're still an apprentice,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:38.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you're something of an art dealer, Kawafuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.52,0:01:41.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you only praising the size \Nbecause you don't know any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:43.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is the size the only \Nthing praiseworthy about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:45.87,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still a real pain in the ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:47.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:49.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The director should be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:50.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The d—!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.19,0:01:54.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-May I please have a glass of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:56.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're way too nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:58.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:04.01,Barakamon Title,,0000,0000,0000,,I Am in Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:04.01,Barakamon Title Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,1)}Translation:\NYoseo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:10.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to say to the director?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:13.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An apology, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.29,0:02:16.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You returned because he said he'd forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:18.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest depends on your state of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:22.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For what it's worth, I bought a \Ncell phone strap to give him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:25.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A cell phone strap? He's not \Na high school girl, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:28.66,Gotou Limited,,0000,0000,0000,,Exclusive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:28.66,Baramon-kun,,0000,0000,0000,,Baramon-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:28.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And these aren't cute at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:36.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep sighing like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:38.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll bring me down, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:40.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The director is going to \Nlook at my calligraphy soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:46.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do if he lambastes \Nit before I exhibit at Naruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:48.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never be able to recover!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:51.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:53.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought it because you felt \Nconfident about it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:59.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As someone who's known me \Na long time, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be able to tell I wrote that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:07.79,STAR,,0000,0000,0000,,STAR
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:07.79,Name 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Seishuu\NHanda
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:07.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you ask me that way, \NI'm not sure how to answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:11.23,Name 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}Seishuu\NHanda
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:12.12,STAR2,,0000,0000,0000,,STAR
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:12.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think it's good calligraphy. \NVery bold and eye-catching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:15.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would've imagined you \Nwriting anything like it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:16.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my point!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:17.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:20.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't write calligraphy like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:22.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:25.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I don't get what you're trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:26.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I put it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:28.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It just doesn't feel right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:29.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It just happened! I don't know how I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.77,10 Minutes Later,,0000,0000,0000,,10 Minutes Later
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:34.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, you're saying it's a fluke?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:36.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put it so simply!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:38.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's exactly what it is, darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:41.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anybody could write something like \Nthat if they went to the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:44.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing odd about that, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:48.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to beat yourself up over \Nusing a different style than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:51.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You could just describe it as \N"a little experimentation."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:55.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I keep doing that, I'll never \Nfind my own calligraphy style.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:04:00.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're studying to be a farmer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:03.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,going fishing on a whim and catching a \Nhisan iwo doesn't make you a fisherman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:07.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to find my own flower \Nand raise it until it blooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:09.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A flower unlike any other in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:12.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The one that was always my special "only one"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:14.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:17.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you implying that you \Ndon't have to be number one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:22.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A farmer cannot become a fisherman, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:25.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a very amusing analogy, Handa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:29.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With both calligraphers and artists,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:33.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the successful ones are those who \Nperfect their own idiosyncrasies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:35.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I didn't come to see you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:38.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I came to meet with Handa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to trouble yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:43.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, are you doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, very well, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:47.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no need to be so formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:50.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You spoke more naturally with me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:52.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I went too far last time, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:58.35,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:05:00.52,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to properly apologize and get his forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:03.53,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,A cane...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:06.49,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The director has a bad back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:14.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, thank you, Handa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:14.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:18.64,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how upset I may have been,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:21.34,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,how could I have hit someone who's like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:24.49,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a horrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:36.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What I did was truly inexcusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have apologized much sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Both for punching you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:45.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and for returning once I \Nknew I would be forgiven,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am truly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:49.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am truly very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:53.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:57.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I wasn't planning on forgiving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:00.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I only said that to lure you back here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:04.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so I could give you a long lecture on human morality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:10.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it appears that won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:15.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just refrain from behaving \Nso impulsively in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:19.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:23.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:27.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't sure what I'd do if you didn't forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:32.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Truly, sir, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:36.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Handa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now give him the cell phone strap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:40.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know this isn't the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Handa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:42.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:45.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to see your calligraphy up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:47.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you lend me a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:48.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:05.02,STAR,,0000,0000,0000,,STAR
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:08.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what you wrote \Nafter taking time to mature?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:09.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:15.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:18.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:21.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:23.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This calligraphy is—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:43.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:39.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I just told you not to behave impulsively...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.23,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh, don't laugh, don't laugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:46.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This calligraphy is a test work! \NThat's right! I drew it for practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:50.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My submission for the exhibition is still \Npacked up, so I couldn't bring it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:52.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:57.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,True, it is unreasonable to expect to see \Nyour work this close to the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:08:01.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir! I'm sorry that I showed \Nyou this trashy calligraphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:03.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Handa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:09.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll appraise this as a test work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:17.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've written something so interesting, \NI wouldn't have recognized it as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:22.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The character is one you'd see \Nin a grade school assignment,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:24.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but in it, I can see the stars of the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:28.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It shows the hopelessness of \Nbeing left behind in the dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:31.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,along with the light that's only visible in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:35.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I wouldn't be the only one to judge it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I would deem it worthy of a grand prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:40.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:42.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I really look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:44.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is a test work,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:48.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then I should see some even more \Nwonderful calligraphy at Naruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:52.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This has been a most fruitful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:54.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop by again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:58.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Director, let me call you a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I've done it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.52,Building Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji House of Art
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:09.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:11.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:13.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My ride is waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:16.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:18.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:24.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So he came by car...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that car...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:38.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that sending Seishuu-kun\N to the island was the correct decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:41.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He still has a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:43.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:47.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, the engine stalled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:49.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not very good at starting up slopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:52.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're both awkward,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,my son and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:10:00.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm scared! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:01.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Handa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:04.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like your dad was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:09.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ship me back to the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:24.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My, it's been quite a while, Kawafuji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:32.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:42.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:44.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:48.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away, cold-hearted jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:52.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by how you look,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:54.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guessing you haven't gotten anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:55.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:57.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that on your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:11:00.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An attempt to get back the \Nform you had on the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:01.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:04.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd give me at least a little inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:07.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The deadline for the exhibition is tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:09.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to be doing stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:12.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have to scold me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:16.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried writing "Star" in the same way as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:19.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, with that flavor, \Nyou could aim for grand prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:21.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wrote it the exact \Nsame way, then it's a cinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.62,MX Calligraphy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40}STAR
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.62,Name 4,,0000,0000,0000,,Seishuu\NHanda
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:27.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it really is like a grade school assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:33.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to write it exactly \Nthe same way, but I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:35.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard I stare at the night sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:38.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the city lights are too bright for me to get anxious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:40.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't write! I can't! I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it this much different from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:48.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It turns out I'm more influenced \Nby my environment than I ever knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were only stable before
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:53.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,because you'd never had any \Nmajor distress in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've always entered \Nexhibitions before, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:58.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:11:59.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:03.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would I bother calling someone like you \Nover if I could manage this by myself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:06.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Someone like you"? How could \Nyou say that to your only friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:08.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do f—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:09.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:13.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is but one thing you can do for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:18.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sei-san, the tea is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:32.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the point of this, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:32.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold still! I can't tie it if you're moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:35.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, who am I supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:37.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even like children that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:39.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:41.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to do is keep quiet and cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:44.15,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bondage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:47.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, might you be Sensei's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:48.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon the intrusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:49.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:51.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sei-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:53.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:55.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! This isn't what it looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:56.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's to help me write calligraphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:12:59.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, Kawafuji-san is playing Naru-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:13:00.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, it's not like that, Mom! Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:01.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,while I'm a crybaby first grader!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:18.06,MX Handwritten,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fad(940,1)}Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.46,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He used to be a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.46,0:13:06.29,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Though never very sociable,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.29,0:13:10.96,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,he was kind at heart, the type young people \Nwould call "prickly-sweet," and beloved by all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:13.59,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, now he's become "prickly-stupid"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:15.69,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither part of that is lovable at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:18.06,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all because he went to that island!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:21.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:22.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:25.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:27.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:29.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,this just felt very reminiscent of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:34.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't it simplistic to \Nexpect to write good calligraphy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:37.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,just by reenacting things you did on the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:39.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:45.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just ditch the calligraphy you could only write \Non the island, and hurry back here to Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:46.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Quit digging around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you had a porn stash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:49.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:50.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:50.60,Calligrapher,,0000,0000,0000,,Calligrapher
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:55.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't throw it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:59.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not in the exhibition, Sensei, \Nthen I don't feel like doing it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:02.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The prize money isn't all that much,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:05.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's not like it'd make me really famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:07.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll write a bunch and \Nhold a one-man exhibition...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:09.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:12.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize how much I have \Nriding on this exhibition?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:15.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, it's not a major exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:21.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But to me, it's a crucial first step \Ntoward a new start in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:23.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely take that step.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:30.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you recording?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:33.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My famous quotes collection!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:35.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you call this kid over, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:38.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought just Naru wouldn't be \Nenough to bring out the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:38.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:39.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's irritating me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:43.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thanks to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:46.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,now I can see how serious you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:50.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's some help from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:51.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:56.24,MX Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:57.62,MX Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,In Call
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:57.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:59.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Is he on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:03.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did he answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:04.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:06.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! You good?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:07.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Put me on, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:09.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:10.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:14.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! Sensei, you doin' good?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:19.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji-san asked us to talk to \Nyou because you seemed lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:21.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Akki! Ain't ya done talkin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:23.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So we all gathered at the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Are you well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:28.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawa-san may be nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:32.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but Hiro-nii is deeply worried about you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:34.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you talking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:35.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:36.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:39.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you left without saying anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:39.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:41.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it's been nuts over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:41.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:42.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:44.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about th—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you doing well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:50.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit sayin' pointless stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'm gonna feed ya my fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:54.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What you need most are friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:56.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:57.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, me next!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:15:59.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:00.60,Phone 2,,0000,0000,0000,,In Call
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:00.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:00.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:04.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Are you well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:02.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:05.65,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He actually thanked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:09.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts my ears! Take turns talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:12.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, yer comin' back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:15.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When're ya comin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:18.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought up a good punishment for \Nya leavin' without sayin' anythin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:20.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:21.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Akki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:22.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Akki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:26.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you were distressed over \Nnot being able to do good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:29.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe how considerate you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:32.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your consideration would put adults to shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:38.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll be fine, if I can stir up some \Ninspiration by remembering the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:41.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Y-Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:44.56,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He's seriously discussing his worries with a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:47.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not exactly in a slump,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:50.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I need to write, I just can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:51.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:54.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Tell me before you switch, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're messing with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:57.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:16:59.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:00.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Naru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:00.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:04.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's borin' without you here, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:07.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still gobs of stuff I wanna do with ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:09.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An' so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come home real soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:18.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're waitin' for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:29.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Think you can write now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:29.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:32.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.29,0:17:39.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, are you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:42.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not sure if I brought it with me or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:46.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but since it was from the last \Njob I did there, then maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:55.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A list of names?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:17:59.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ink...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:02.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grind me lots of ink!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:05.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki, go buy paper for writing practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:06.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:11.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, he's taking action.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:13.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope he doesn't do anything strange again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:16.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was against this from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:19.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want him going to that island again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:21.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you should persuade him not to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.21,0:18:23.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's already decided he wants to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:28.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to hurt him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:29.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:32.87,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Cruel! Cruel! Cruel! Cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:35.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We also share the responsibility for \NSei becoming "all work and no play."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:39.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not for us to dictate \Nour son's direction in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:42.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If leaving here will allow him to grow,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:46.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then all we can do is watch over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:51.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear... If that's the path a man must take...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:54.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! It's Handa Seimei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:56.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so dignified! So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:58.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you quit it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:37.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wake up, Kawafuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:41.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.92,0:19:44.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:48.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A work done using all my ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:57.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it incredible?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:59.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never done calligraphy like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:01.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the title?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:05.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Stone Wall."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:42.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they've displayed our summer \Nvacation homework in the hallway!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:45.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:46.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's come...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:49.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:51.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:54.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet we'll win gold prizes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:57.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei would be so thrilled if we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:22:00.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get double-gold and \Ngive him a big surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:04.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei'd better thank God for \Ngivin' him such capable disciples!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:06.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:07.88,Gold Prize,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Prize
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:07.88,Tamako,,0000,0000,0000,,Class 2-1 Arai Tamako
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:11.55,MX Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Learning From the Past
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:11.55,Miwa,,0000,0000,0000,,Class 2-1\NYamamura\NMiwa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:11.55,Silver1,,0000,0000,0000,,Silver
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:14.97,Silver2,,0000,0000,0000,,Silver
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:18.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Miwa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.99,0:22:20.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.15,0:22:31.25,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Why only Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:38.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa-chan, just snap out of it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.15,0:22:39.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.23,0:22:41.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't face Sensei now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:43.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with a silver prize?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:44.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still second place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:48.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a world of difference \Nbetween first and second!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.02,0:22:49.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}that{\i0} mad?!
